Package: deflex
Title: Yet Another Differential Evolution Package
Version: 0.0.2
Authors@R: person("Vehbi Sinan", "Tunalioglu", email="vst@vsthost.com", role=c("aut", "cre"))
Description: There are 3.5 Differential Evolution (DE) packages for R
    as of the moment this package has been initiated. This package,
    however, provides functional control over the selection, crossover
    and mutation operator bringing greater flexibility for
    experimenting with documented and custom DE strategies.
License: GPL-3
